name: Linska
cleanBio: Linska is a rising star in the electronic music scene. She made waves with her first collaboration with renowned Irish producer Rebūke on the track ‘Digital Dream’. With her innovative approach and undeniable talent, Linska is quickly becoming a name to watch; known for her unique style blending tech house and techno, she has been captivating audiences all over the world with her dark sound, distinctive vocals and driving basslines.
